### Q4. What is the difference between Real DOM and Virtual DOM?

**Answer:**

| Feature           | Real DOM                          | Virtual DOM                         |
| ----------------- | --------------------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| What is it?       | The actual browser DOM            | A JavaScript copy of the DOM       |
| Speed             | Slow to update                    | Fast to update                      |
| Updates           | Re-renders entire DOM tree        | Updates only changed parts          |
| Memory            | High memory consumption           | Lightweight                         |
| Manipulation      | Directly manipulates the browser  | Manipulates in memory first         |
| Cost              | Expensive re-painting/re-flowing  | Minimal re-painting                 |

