### Q6. What is the difference between Functional and Class Components?

**Answer:**

| Feature              | Functional Component           | Class Component                  |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------ | -------------------------------- |
| Syntax               | Plain JavaScript function      | ES6 class with `render()`        |
| State                | `useState` hook                | `this.state` + `this.setState`   |
| Lifecycle            | `useEffect` hook               | `componentDidMount`, etc.        |
