### Q52. What is the difference between `Link` and `<a>` tag in React?

**Answer:**

| Feature          | `<Link to="/">` (React Router) | `<a href="/">`              |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------ | --------------------------- |
| Navigation       | Client-side (no page reload)   | Full page reload            |
| Performance      | ✅ Fast (SPA navigation)       | ❌ Slow (re-downloads everything) |
| State preserved  | ✅ Yes                
